FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>5:11:49 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">BB/Uber/Whatever</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Exactly how is this being enforced/monitored?  So far it seems like if you're buddy-buddy with a BB guild you just call them in, or that whoever is first to say &quot;Need help?  Ok we're coming to kill Cazic/Innoruuk&quot; is the group that goes.<br>
